# docs/ai layout

| Path | Put here |
|------|----------|
| `docs/ai/designs/` | `*_DESIGN.md`, `*_IMPLEMENTATION.md` |
| `docs/ai/adrs/` | `ADR-*.md` |
| `docs/ai/bugs/` | `BUG-*.md` |
| `docs/ai/sessions/` | Session notes |
| `docs/ai/templates/` | Templates only — do not edit in place for real work |
| `docs/course/` | Course PDF/images — read-only reference |

New Feature: copy template → fill Meta → register FEATURE_REGISTRY first.

Do not put Verilog in `docs/`. Do not put design prose in `rtl/`.
